===[[Asian Games]]===
{{Main|Boxing at the Asian Games}}

====2006 Doha Asian Games====
{{Main|Boxing at the 2006 Asian Games}}
Seven amateur athletes represented Mongolia in this edition of the [[Asiad]] winning to rank in the medal tally.<ref>[http://doha-2006.com Boxing standings]</ref>

====Entry list====
* Tuvshinbat Byamba ([[Light Welterweight]])
* [[Enkhbatyn Badar-Uugan]] ([[Bantamweight]]) - Bronze
* Otgonbayar Jigjid ([[Light Flyweight]])
* Serdamba Purevdorj ([[Flyweight]])
* Chuluuntumur Tumurhuyag ([[Welterweight]])
* [[Uranchimegiin M<U+00F6>nkh-Erdene]] (Lightweight) - Silver
* Enkhzorig Zorgitbaatar ([[Featherweight]]) - Silver

